dys Knight & the Pips|The Pips]] ([[Gladys Knight]]) * [[The Raelettes]] ([[Ray Charles]]) * [[The Revolution (band)|The Revolution]] ([[Prince (musician)|Prince]]) * [[The Rumour]] ([[Graham Parker]]) * [[The Section (band)|The Section]] ([[Jackson Browne]], [[James Taylor]]) * [[Jonathan Davis and the SFA|The SFA]] ([[Jonathan Davis]]) * [[The Shadows]] ([[Cliff Richard]]) * [[The Shondells]] ([[Tommy James]]) * [[Stephen Kellogg and the Sixers|The Sixers]] ([[Stephen Kellogg and the Sixers|Stephen Kellogg]]) * [[The Spiders from Mars]] ([[David Bowie]]) * [[The Steep Canyon Rangers]] ([[Steve Martin]]) * [[The Stooges]] ([[Iggy Pop]]) * [[The Strangers (American band)|The Strangers]] ([[Merle Haggard]]) * [[KC and the Sunshine Band|The Sunshine Band]] ([[Harry Wayne Casey|KC]]) * [[The Supremes]] ([[Diana Ross]]) * [[The Tennessee Three]] ([[Johnny Cash]]) * [[The Vandellas]] ([[Martha Reeves]]) * [[Richard Hell and the Voidoids|The Voidoids]] ([[Richard Hell]]) * [[The Wailers (1963-1974 band)|The Wailers]] ([[Bob Marley]]) * [[Katrina and The Waves|The Waves]] ([[Katrina Leskanich]]) * [[Tupper Ware Remix Party]] ([[Ninja Sex Party]]) * [[Union Station (band)|Union Station]] ([[Alison Krauss]]) {{div col end}}
