The tower was the first TV tower in the Netherlands, and is currently owned by [[Alticom]], but the area around the tower is owned by [[KPN]], whilst the antenna is owned by [[NOVEC]]. In 2007 a new antenna was installed, which is {{convert|11|m|ft|1}} shorter than the previous antenna.
