{{Refimprove|date=February 2015}} The '''National Board of Review Award for Best Animated Feature''' is one of the annual awards given (since 2000) by the [[National Board of Review|National Board of Review of Motion Pictures]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nationalboardofreview.org/award-names/best-animated-feature/|title=Best Animated Feature Archives – National Board of Review|work=[[National Board of Review]]|accessdate=February 2, 2015}}</ref> Every year from 2001 to 2004 and from 2007 to 2011, the award was given to the film that would eventually receive the [[Academy Award for Best Animated Feature|Academy Award counterpart]].{{citation needed|date=December 2017}}
==Winners==
