'''Selecciones Ilustradas''' (sometimes known as ''S.I.'') is a Spanish art agency founded by [[Josep Toutain]].
==Warren Publishing== Selecciones Ilustradas is probably most well known in America due to its connections with [[Warren Publishing]], where S.I.'s artists drew hundreds of stories between 1971 through 1983. The deal with Warren and S.I. began in 1971 when Toutain met with Warren publisher [[James Warren (publisher)|Jim Warren]].<ref name="WC1">{{Cite book| year=2001 |author1=Roach, David A. |author2=Jon B. Cooke |lastauthoramp=yes | title=The Warren Companion|page=129|publisher=Two Morrows Publishing| ISBN = 978-1-893905-08-5}}</ref> S.I.'s artists began appearing in Warren magazines starting in [[Vampirella]] 11 in May 1971.<ref name="WC2">{{Cite book| year=2001 |author1=Roach, David A. |author2=Jon B. Cooke |lastauthoramp=yes | title=The Warren Companion|page=257|publisher=Two Morrows Publishing| ISBN = 978-1-893905-08-5}}</ref> By 1973 S.I. artists provided the majority of the covers and interior stories in Warren's magazines, a dominance that continued until the late 1970s. S.I. artists also contributed to Warren rival [[Skywald]] throughout the early to mid-1970s.
==Artists== Artists associated with Selecciones Ilustradas include:<ref name="WC3">{{Cite book| year=2001 |author1=Roach, David A. |author2=Jon B. Cooke |lastauthoramp=yes | title=The Warren Companion|pages=257–265|publisher=Two Morrows Publishing| ISBN = 978-1-893905-08-5}}</ref> {| border="0" cellpadding="2" | valign="top" | * [[Juan Antonio Abellán]] * [[Vicente Alcazar]] * [[Artur Aldomà Puig]] * [[César Álvarez Cañete]], ''Zesar'' * [[Pedro Añaños]] * [[Rafael Aura León]], ''Auraleon'' * [[Alfonso Azpiri]] * [[Ángel Badía Camps]] * [[Enric Badia Romero]] * [[Jordi Badia Romero]] * [[Josep María Beá]] * [[Luis Bermejo]] * [[Emilio Bernardó]] * [[Jordi Bernet]] * [[Aurelio Bevia]] * [[Jesús Blasco]] * [[Joaquín Blázquez]] * [[Daniel Branca]] * [[Joan Beltrán Bofill]] * [[Jaime Brocal Remohí]] * [[José María Cardona Blasi]] * [[Emilia Castañeda Martínez]] * [[Florenci Clavé]] * [[Luis Collado Coch]] * [[Antonio Colmeiro]] * [[Francisco Cueto]] * [[Jesús Durán]] * [[Ramón Escolano]] * [[Fernando Fernández (comics)|Fernando Fernández]] * [[Manel Ferrer]], ''Manel'' * [[Alfons Figueras]] | valign="top" | * [[Alfonso Font]] * [[Chiqui de la Fuente]] * [[Víctor de la Fuente]] * [[Miguel Fuster]] * [[Jorge Gálvez Badía]] * [[Amador García Cabrera]] * [[Luis García Mozos]] * [[José García Pizarro]] * [[Carlos Giménez (comics)|Carlos Giménez]] * [[Juan Giménez]] * [[Eugenio Giner]] * [[Jordi Ginés Soteras]], ''Gin'' * [[Domingo Gómez Álvarez]] * [[José González (artist)|José González Navarro]] (Pepe González) * [[Francisco González Vilanova]] * [[Göte Goranssön]] * [[Rafael Griera Calderón]] * [[Josep Gual i Tutusaus]] * [[Fernando Güell]] * [[Francisco Guinovart Rotllán]] * [[Eloy Jiménez]] * [[Jaime Juez i Castellà]], ''Xirinius'' * [[Jorge Longarón]] * [[José Lombardía]] * [[Rafael Losada]] * [[Rafael López Espí]] * [[César López Vera]] * [[Esteban Maroto]] * [[Santiago Martín Salvador]] * [[Joan Martí]], ''Petronius'' * [[José María Martín Sauri]] | valign="top" | * [