==In fiction== The cartoonist [[Carlos Giménez (comics)|Carlos Giménez]] wrote a fictionalized account on his stint at the studios in his series ''{{illm|Los profesionales|lt=Los profesionales|es|Los profesionales (historieta de Carlos Giménez)}}'', where a thinly-veiled depiction of the studio was given the name ''Creaciones Ilustradas''.
