The '''Swiss Film Archive''' (French: ''Cinémathèque suisse'', German: ''Schweizer Filmarchiv'') is a [[Switzerland|Swiss]] state-approved noncommercial foundation based in [[Lausanne]].
Its aims are to collect, protect, study and present film archives.<ref>{{fr}} [http://www.cinematheque.ch/f/la-cinematheque/mission/ Mission], www.cinematheque.ch (page visited on 20 April 2013).</ref>
